description: [CAF] Tanzanian side Young Africans reignited their bid for a place in the knockout rounds of the TotalEnergies CAF Champions League with a 3-1 home victory over TP Mazembe this past weekend, boosted by a brace of goals from Clement Mzize.
title: Africa: CAF Interclub Player of the Week - Clement Mzize

description: [Premium Times] The visit of the Chinese Foreign Minister and the renewed push for alliance from China offers another opportunity for African nations to reposition for a more impactful engagement and value-added partnership.
title: Africa: Chinese Foreign Minister's Africa Tour Points to Appetite for Natural Resources

description: [New Dawn] In a significant step towards addressing Liberia's electricity deficit and advancing renewable energy, the Ministry of Mines and Energy (MME), National Investment Commission (NIC), and Ministry of Justice (MOJ) have signed a Memorandum of Understanding (MOU) with Arthur Energy Africa (AEA) to conduct comprehensive studies towards the development of the hydropower potential of the St. John River Basin.
title: Africa: GOL Signs MOU With Arthur Energy Africa to Develop Hydropower Scheme On St. John River
